MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 324

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF MARAGUSAN NATIONAL HIGH SCHOOL A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN, SITUATED IN POBLACION, MARAGUSAN, COMPOSTELA VALLEY PROVINCE, ISLAND OF MINDANAO

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, JOSEPH EJERCITO ESTRADA, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale, entry, disposition or settlement, and reserve for school site purposes of Maragusan National High School under the administration of the Department of Education, Culture and Sports, subject to private rights, if any there be, a certain parcel of land of the public domain situated in Poblacion, Municipality of Maragusan, Compostela Valley Province, Island of Mindanao, and more particularly described as follows:

Lot 143, TS-11-000074-D (Maragusan National High School) San Mariano Townsite Subdivision

A PARCEL OF LAND, Lot 143, Ts-11-000074-D, situated in Poblacion, Municipality of Maragusan, Compostela Valley Province, Island of Mindanao.

Bounded on the N., along line 26-27; E., along lines 27-28-1, both of Lot 716, TS-11-000045-D, Mansaca Villagers; along lines 1-2-3-4-5-6-7 by Road (20.00 m. wide); S., along line 7-8 by Lot 126; along line 8-9 by Lot 127; along line 9-10 by Lot 128; along line 10-11 by Lot 129; along line 11-12 by Lot 130; along line 12-13 by Lot 131; along line 13-14 by Lot 132; along line 14-15 by Lot 133; along line 15-16 by Lot 134; along line 16-17 by Lot 135; along line 17-18 by Lot 136; along line 18-19 by Lot 137; along line 19-20 by Lot 138; along line 20-21 by Lot 139; along line 21-22 by Lot 140; along line 22-23 by Lot 141; along line 23-24 by Lot 142, all of TS-11-000074-D; W., along line 24-25 by Lot 138; and along line 25-26 by Lot 136; both of Mabini Public Land Subdivision, Pls-633. Tie Line:

